Available_Say_Animations_Prefix.en:
Available talk animations for [:talk(say("text", talk_animation))] (format: mode_animation or animation):
{SayAnimationList}
Examples: 'happy_shy' (shy animation in happy mode), 'nomal_say' (say animation in normal mode), 'shy' (shy animation in current mode)

Available_Say_Animations_Prefix.zh:
可用的说话动画 [:talk(say("文本", 说话动画))] (格式: 状态_动画 或 动画):
{SayAnimationList}
示例: 'happy_shy' (开心状态下的害羞动画), 'nomal_say' (普通状态下的说话动画), 'shy' (当前状态下的害羞动画)
